轻症患者家属自述：冠状病毒肺炎很可恨，但没那么可怕。
Family members of patients with mild illness said: coronavirus pneumonia is hateful, but not so terrible.
周纯。
Zhou Chun.
腾讯深网                      。
Tencent deep net.
