作者 | 周纯 出品|棱镜·腾讯小满工作室新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情下，人们担心自己会被周围未知的病毒携带者感染，更担心万一感染之后，能否治愈？是否会像当年“非典“一样留下后遗症？《棱镜》1月25日对话了一名新型冠状病毒肺炎确诊病人的家属，她老公不久前在北京被确诊。
With the new coronavirus pneumonia at Rita Prism Tencent, people are worried about being infected by unknown virus carriers around them and whether they will be cured if they get infected.
不幸中的万幸，由于他老公抵抗力不错，又发现得很早，属于轻症患者，目前状态平稳。
Unfortunate in the lucky, because his husband's resistance is good, and found very early, belongs to the light disease patient, the current state is stable.
她选择向大家讲述自己这段时间的亲身经历：冠状病毒肺炎没有想象中的可怕，在轻症时及时吃药治疗是管用的，正常的治疗也不会采用大量激素导致后遗症。
She chose to tell you her own experience of this period: the coronavirus pneumonia is not imagined terrible, in the light of timely drug treatment is useful, normal treatment will not use a lot of hormones resulting in sequelae.
但它的可恨之处在于，传染性非常强，只要体质稍微弱一点就容易被传染。
But it is hateful because it is very infectious, as long as slightly weaker constitution is easy to be infected.
以下为她的自述原文，《棱镜》做了部分删减：老公症状不典型但确诊，我主动去检查隔离我们家住北京，老公一月中旬赴武汉出差，回来后当时就有非常轻微的感冒症状，浑身发冷，期间吃了三天白加黑，无好转，还是浑身乏力、发冷。
When my husband came back from a business trip to Wuhan in the middle of January, he had very mild cold symptoms, and he had a cold all over his body.
虽然这其间老公不咳嗽、不发烧、不胸闷，之前也没有检查出来什么问题，只是开了几款感冒常用药品。
Although the husband did not cough, fever, chest tightness, before also did not detect any problems, just opened a few common cold medicines.
后来，老公开始有点发烧，在医生朋友的指点下，他又去了另一家有病毒核酸检测试剂的三甲医院，肺部CT显示为肺炎，试剂结果显示为阳性，医院初步确诊为新型冠状病毒肺炎。
Later, my husband began to have a fever, under the doctor's friend's guidance, he went to another three-A hospital with viral nucleic acid reagent, lung CT showed pneumonia, reagent results showed positive, the hospital initially diagnosed as a new coronavirus pneumonia.
初步确诊之后，老公被留院隔离，由区疾控中心继续复查，一天之后，复查结果显示确诊；然后上报市疾控中心进行专家会诊，最后公布确诊，统一转院，由专门的传染病医院进行治疗。
After the initial diagnosis, the husband was kept in isolation, by the District CDC continued to review, a day later, the results of the review results confirmed; and then reported to the CDC for expert consultation, final announcement confirmed, unified referral hospital, specialized infectious disease hospitals for treatment.
值得一提的是，在这个过程中，老公依然不发烧、不咳嗽、不胸闷。
It is worth mentioning, in this process, husband still does not have a fever, cough, do not chest tightness.
确诊的那几天，面临各方面的压力，我自己在家大哭了几次，处于崩溃的边缘。
I was on the verge of collapse after crying at home several times during the first few days of diagnosis.
知道冠状病毒肺炎的传染性极强，作为与患者密切接触的家属，我主动前往医院进行全方位的检查，幸运的是，经过医院以及各级疾控中心会诊后，我的所有检测指标均为阴性，但即便是这样，我也一直被隔离在医院，其重视程度可见一斑。
Knowing that coronavirus pneumonia is highly infectious, as close contacts with the family, I took the initiative to go to the hospital for a full examination, Fortunately, after the hospital and CDC consultation, all my indicators are negative, but even so, I have been isolated in the hospital, the degree of importance attached to it.
正常治疗状态平稳，不要相信网上传言老公留院观察的那一天，输了一整天液，第二天只吃了一片拜复乐。
Normal treatment state is stable, do not believe that the day my husband stay in the hospital to observe the day, lost a day of fluid, the next day only ate a piece of music.
在转到传染病医院治疗时，医院开了两种中成药：肺力咳和莲花清瘟颗粒。
When transferred to the hospital for treatment of infectious diseases, the hospital prescribed two proprietary Chinese medicines: pulmonary cough and lotus rinderpest granules.
所以，不要去相信“医院肯定会采用大量激素治疗，导致股骨头坏死之类”的网上传言，实际上，正常的治疗不会采用大量激素。
So don't believe that "hospitals are bound to use a lot of hormone therapy, which can lead to necrosis of the femoral head." In fact, normal treatments do not use a lot of hormones.
我老公40来岁，平时抵抗力还可以，只是前阵子一直在出差，身体很疲惫，估计处于比较容易感染病毒的状态。
My husband is 40 years old, normal resistance is OK, just a while ago has been on business, the body is very tired, is estimated to be at a relatively easy to infected with the virus.
这也是冠状病毒很可恨的地方，体质稍微弱一点，抵抗力差一点就容易被传染上。
This is also the coronavirus is hateful place, slightly weaker constitution, resistance is easy to be infected.
由于我有了亲身经历，这几天身边很多有生病症状的朋友都来问我，让我帮忙看看是不是冠状病毒肺炎，我想说，不用过于紧张，不是所有头痛脑热都是由这个病毒引起的，大家要冷静判断，这个病在轻症时确实都可以居家治疗。
Due to my personal experience, many of my friends with symptoms of illness have come to me these days and asked me to help see if it is coronavirus pneumonia. I would like to say that not all head-to-head fever is caused by this virus.
目前我老公症状比较轻，吃了药，状态比较平稳，未来也需要经过多次检查，确定康复才能出院。
At present my husband's symptoms are relatively light, take medicine, the state is relatively stable, the future also needs to go through many checks, to determine convalescence before discharge.
目前全家都在及时监测汇报中现在，疾控中心、社区卫生站每天都会打电话问情况，疾控中心人员还指导我对家里进行全面消毒杀菌。
Now, CDC, community health stations are calling every day, and CDC staff also instruct me to disinfect and sterilize my home.
出于责任，我对周围朋友、邻居也提了老公患病事实，以提示大家不用紧张，客观应对。
Out of responsibility, I also to the surrounding friends, neighbors also mentioned the fact that her husband was ill, to remind everyone not to be nervous, objective response.
我愿意出来说的最主要的目的，还是希望大家能对自己对家庭对别人都负责，不恐慌不夸大。
I would like to say that the main purpose is to hope that everyone can be responsible for their own family and others, do not panic exaggerate.
理性看待，保护好自己和家人。
Think rationally and protect yourself and your family.
如果不幸遇到，则正向冷静去应对。
If you encounter misfortune, you are dealing with it calmly.
。
.
发送到看一看 。
Send it to see.
